### 17. Inflation starts at 1.0 in year 0 regardless of start year
**Module:** `simulation.py` ~lines 144, 179-181
**Type:** CLARIFICATION_NEEDED

Tax brackets use 2024 base values with no inflation adjustment in year 0. If someone sets `start_year=2030`, the brackets should reflect 6 years of inflation from 2024, but they don't.

**Fix:** Either pre-inflate brackets by `(start_year - 2024)` years, or document that brackets assume the simulation starts in 2024 dollars.

